{
  "stem": "24614.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the community was one, though, when it came to anything to help, to do, to celebrate.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a very big Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, before Hitler, there were 50,000 Jews in Antwerp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And 5,000 remained alive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I am one of the 5,000.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, as far as I know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I-- the only thing I can remember is the school, a public school, where my mother and all of us mixed with everybody.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I didn't feel anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember my street.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It wasn't all Jewish, but most of them were Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I didn't feel that I was different, better, or somebody else was not as good-- and my teachers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The rest, I remember my daddy having partners who were not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I never heard him say anything derogatory about them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Or if he did, I didn't hear it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only thing I know that-- I was brought up from when I was six or seven, I belonged to a youth group, to a Zionist youth group.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Each one of us in my house belonged to different youth groups.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One was more Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One was socialistic, and so on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we, we-- our goal was once, when we grow up, to see Palestine then, of course, and maybe to live there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my friends, and my ideals, and my, my looking to my future of my life, was one day to be with Jews.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was no other question.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Even if I stay in Antwerp, I will-- my dearest friends and my nearest friends will be Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I was with them in the-- I went to camp with them in the summer.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I played with them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I hiked with them.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
